        <div id="dsq-comment-body-214" class="dsq-comment-body">
            <div id="dsq-comment-message-214" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>This was a great summary of your experience, thank you for taking the time to put it out there. It&#8217;s hard to leave a support structure, especially if it&#8217;s as big as it sounds, and I trust you won&#8217;t look back on this decision negatively.</p>
